main_body:
In Article 1 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3815/87, the second and third indents are hereby replaced by the following:
'- 3 000 tonnes of bone-in beef held by the intervention agency of the United Kingdom and bought in before 1 June 1987;
- 9 000 tonnes of bone-in beef held by the Irish intervention agency, and bought in before 1 January 1987;'.
